<div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-50/70 via-white to-slate-50/70 dark:from-gray-900 dark:via-gray-900 dark:to-slate-900">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-blue-100/70 dark:border-gray-800">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 animate-gradient opacity-20 dark:opacity-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-56 w-56 translate-x-1/3 -translate-y-1/4 rounded-full bg-blue-300/30 blur-3xl dark:bg-blue-500/10"></div>
    <div class="container relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-14 md:py-20">
      <div class="animate-fade-up">
        <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-blue-200/70 bg-white/80 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-blue-700 shadow-sm backdrop-blur dark:border-blue-700/40 dark:bg-gray-900/80 dark:text-blue-300">
          <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500"></span>
          ABOUT THIS APP
        </p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
          シンプルで、<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-sky-500 to-indigo-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">心地よい</span>ブログ体験を
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          Rails と Tailwind CSS で作ったポートフォリオ兼ブログアプリです。読みやすさと操作の気持ちよさを大切に、
          余白・配色・動きのバランスを丁寧に設計しています。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-10 md:py-14">
    <article class="space-y-8">
      <section class="animate-fade-up rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 bg-white/85 p-6 shadow-sm backdrop-blur dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800/65 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">制作で意識したこと</h2>
        <div class="mt-5 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50/70 p-4 dark:border-blue-900/60 dark:bg-blue-900/20">
            <p class="font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300">シンプルさ</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">余計な要素を削ぎ落とし、コンテンツが主役になる構成を目指しました。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-sky-100 bg-sky-50/70 p-4 dark:border-sky-900/60 dark:bg-sky-900/20">
            <p class="font-semibold text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300">一貫性</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">配色・余白・タイポグラフィを統一し、迷わないUIトーンを維持しています。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-indigo-100 bg-indigo-50/70 p-4 dark:border-indigo-900/60 dark:bg-indigo-900/20">
            <p class="font-semibold text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300">使いやすさ</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">直感的な導線とわかりやすいラベルで、ストレスのない操作を意識しました。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-violet-100 bg-violet-50/70 p-4 dark:border-violet-900/60 dark:bg-violet-900/20">
            <p class="font-semibold text-violet-700 dark:text-violet-300">アクセシビリティ</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">コントラストやフォントサイズ、キーボード操作にも配慮しています。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-5 rounded-lg border border-amber-200/80 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-amber-700 dark:border-amber-900/60 dark:bg-amber-900/20 dark:text-amber-300">
          ダークモード — 目に優しいダークテーマを用意し、設定で切り替え可能にしました。（本番環境調整中）
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="animate-fade-up rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 bg-white/85 p-6 shadow-sm backdrop-blur dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800/65 md:p-8" style="animation-delay: 0.08s">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">使用技術</h2>
        <div class="mt-5 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Backend</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Ruby on Rails 8.1</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Frontend</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Tailwind CSS 4, Hotwire (Turbo, Stimulus)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Database</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">SQLite / PostgreSQL (Production)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Infra</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Docker, Render</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="animate-fade-up rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 bg-white/85 p-6 shadow-sm backdrop-blur dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800/65 md:p-8" style="animation-delay: 0.16s">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">主な機能</h2>
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-blue-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-blue-700 dark:bg-blue-900/40 dark:text-blue-300">投稿CRUD</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-700 dark:bg-emerald-900/40 dark:text-emerald-300">カテゴリ管理</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-violet-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-violet-700 dark:bg-violet-900/40 dark:text-violet-300">キーワード検索</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-amber-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-amber-700 dark:bg-amber-900/40 dark:text-amber-300">カテゴリ絞り込み</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-sky-700 dark:bg-sky-900/40 dark:text-sky-300">ダークモード</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-pink-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-pink-700 dark:bg-pink-900/40 dark:text-pink-300">レスポンシブ</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="animate-fade-up pt-2" style="animation-delay: 0.24s">
        <%= link_to root_path, class: "inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-blue-200 bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-blue-600 shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-blue-300 hover:text-blue-700 dark:border-blue-800/60 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-blue-300 dark:hover:border-blue-700" do %>
          <span>←</span>
          トップに戻る
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</div>
